Conventions:
1. variable name: all variable names wii be all lowercase, if you want to add another word to your variable name,
                  add an underscore _ and then the other word.
                  Example: dan_buganim
                  
2. functions name: the same as variable name

3. class name: all class names should start with uppercase and all class names should have only one word in it

4. commenting: every sections of your code must be commented in order to make everyone's life easier.
